description:
The nightmare is almost over, everyone! Join me, MauLer, Star Wars Theory, Baggage Claim and Tyrone Magnus as we discuss the penultimate episode of The Acolyte, Kotaku melting down almost as fast as they're closing down, and share our thoughts on the Gladiator 2 trailer. 

Check out Theory Sabers: https://www.theorysabers.com
Sub to Baggage Claim: https://www.youtube.com/@BaggageClaim
Sub to Tyrone Magnus: https://www.youtube.com/@TyroneMagnus
title: Open Bar #103 - Acolyte Self-Destructs, Gladiator 2 Trailer, Kotaku Meltdown
